# ğŸš€ Credit Card Fraud Detection with Flask & Anomaly Detection

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
This is a **Credit Card Fraud Detection** system built with **Flask** and **Machine Learning**.  
It uses **Anomaly Detection Techniques** to identify fraudulent transactions and sends **email alerts** to the user.  

ğŸ”¹ **Tech Stack:** Flask, Python, Scikit-Learn, Chart.js, SMTP (Email Alerts)  
ğŸ”¹ **Features:**
- âœ… Detects suspicious transactions using a trained ML model
- âœ… Sends **email alerts** for fraud transactions
- âœ… Displays fraud detection statistics using **Chart.js**
- âœ… Web-based UI for user interaction

