## ğŸ“Œ Dataset Information
This project is based on the **Kaggle Credit Card Fraud Dataset**, which contains **Time, Amount, and transaction details.**  
ğŸ”— **Dataset Link:** [https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mlg-ulb/creditcardfraud](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mlg-ulb/creditcardfraud)

| Feature  | Description |
|----------|------------|
| **Time** | Seconds since first transaction |
| **Amount** | Transaction amount in USD |
| **Class** | `0 = Normal`, `1 = Fraud` |

